  "body": "There is nothing in ERC2981 that disallows to burn royalties.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/57725120581e27ec469e1c7e497a4008aafff818/contracts/token/common/ERC2981.sol#L100\r\n\r\nThe implementation could verify that `royalty.royaltyFraction != 0` for a token  instead of `royalty.receiver != address(0)` to decide if it needs to check for default royalties here: \r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/57725120581e27ec469e1c7e497a4008aafff818/contracts/token/common/ERC2981.sol#L46\r\n\r\nand allow people to burn royalties if they want to.",
